<P>A: It does.</P>

<P>Q: Okay. Does it also have a signature on there that purports to be the signature of James McDougal?</P>

<P>A: It does.</P>

<P>Q: Okay. Let me ask you, Mr. President, is the signature on Government's Exhibit Number 94 -</P>

