<P>A: No, sir. I have gotten a few phone calls since then. That was more than 10 years ago. I don't remember it, no.</P>

<P>Q: Sir, the records of the governor's mansion of the state of Arkansas reflect that on December 19th, 1985, Mr. McDougal and Senator Fulbright came by the mansion and visited with you. Do you remember that event, sir?</P>

