<P>A: This is a note from Nancy. It says, He needs to see you before Tuesday to get you to sign some personal business papers. The best time would be this weekend or next Monday, which is a state holiday. Any time is fine with Jim. Do you want me to have him come by?'' So, this is between 1-14 and the next Tuesday, and  I said, "Saturday morning."</P>

