<P>A: No.</P>

<P>Q: On April the 3rd, 1986, Master Marketing received $300,000 from David Hale's corporation, Capital Management Services. Were you told in advance, sir, that such a loan was going to be made?</P>

<P>A: No.</P>

<P>Q: Were you told after such a loan was made that it had been made?</P>

<P>A: No.</P>

