<P><a href="/library/government/whitewater/report/white11.html">The Handling of Federal Investigations</a>     309</P>



<P>  <a href="/library/government/whitewater/report/white12.html">The White House Intervention in Federal Investigations</a>     359 </P>

 

<P>          <a href="/library/government/whitewater/report/white13.html">White House Interference with Congressional Inquiries</a>     420 </P>

       

