     B.     Mrs. Clinton's contacts with regulator Beverly Bassett Schaffer     462<BR>

     C.     Mrs. Clinton's role in Madison's proposed preferred stock deal      463<BR>

     D.      Mrs. Clinton's role in the Castle Grande transaction     465</P><BR>



